{"word":"ἀφάνισις","slug":"ἀφάνισις","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀφάνισις</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>From <a href='S:ἀφανίζω'><el>ἀφανίζω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>a getting rid of</i>, <el>τῆς δίκης</el> <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>(from <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>) <i>disappearance</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}